code: import axios from'axios';const API_URL=process.env.REACT_APP_API;export const getStudentTimesheetById=(id,token)=>{return axios.get("".concat(API_URL,"/users/students/").concat(id,"/timesheets"),{headers:{Authorization:"Bearer ".concat(token)}});};export const updateStudentTimesheetById=(id,data,token)=>{return axios.put("".concat(API_URL,"/admin/timesheet/").concat(id),data,{headers:{Authorization:"Bearer ".concat(token)}});};export const deleteStudentTimesheetById=(id,token)=>{return axios.delete("".concat(API_URL,"/admin/timesheet/").concat(id),{headers:{Authorization:"Bearer ".concat(token)}});};
